OL,3,CRSPCA warns the number of people
OL,4,Cabandoning pets is rising
OL,6,FSusie Hughes RSPCA Manchester and
OL,7,FSalford Branch Manager said: "Over the
OL,8,Fcourse of 2025, there's been a 19%
OL,9,Fincrease across the country of calls
OL,10,Ffor abandoned animals to the RSPCA
OL,11,Fhelpline.
OL,13,F"That's a huge amount in one year."
OL,15,FThe RSPCA housed over 3500 animals
OL,16,Fover Christmas, including a record
OL,17,F1500 cats.
