OL,3,CRSPCA warns the number of people
OL,4,Cabandoning pets is rising
OL,6,FElena and Katerina were just 14 weeks
OL,7,Fold when they were taken in by the
OL,8,FRSPCA, and they are hopeful that
OL,9,Fthey'll find them a new home soon.
OL,11,FCharities like the RSPCA say there are
OL,12,Fseveral reasons why animals might be
OL,13,Fabandoned, sometimes a pet could get
OL,14,Finjured and owners could struggle to
OL,15,Fmeet the veterinary costs, or owners
OL,16,Fmight not consider the long term costs
OL,17,Fof looking after pets.
OL,19,FAngela Harrison, RSPCA rehoming
OL,20,Fmanager said shrinkflation has made it
OL,21,Fworse too.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
