OL,3,CRSPCA warns the number of people
OL,4,Cabandoning pets is rising
OL,6,FShe said: "A box of kitten food that
OL,7,Fnow costs #4.50 might only feed a
OL,8,Fkitten for three days, whereas a year
OL,9,Fago that would have lasted four and a
OL,10,Fhalf days so things are definitely
OL,11,Fgetting more expensive for people."
OL,13,FCovid has also had an impact too,
OL,14,FAngela said "We've got generations of
OL,15,Fanimals that haven't been neutered,
OL,16,Fand they're obviously having offspring
OL,17,Fthemselves."
